🚨 FAILURE: IDLE instruction handling bug detected!
Actual behavior:
  Committed PCs: 0x00 -> 0x04 -> 0x08 -> 0x10 -> 0x14 -> 0x18 -> 0x30
Expected behavior:
  Should be: 0x00 -> 0x04 -> 0x08 (then stop)

🚨 ROOT CAUSE: IDLE instruction does not properly stop CPU execution
Evidence of bugs:
  1. IDLE instruction may not be recognized by IFU
  2. Pipeline flush may not occur when IDLE is encountered
  3. Speculative instructions in pipeline are incorrectly committed
